08:26:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">599J強制檢測途徑</span></strong>：<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">（一）於流動採樣站接受檢測服務（名單及服務對象：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=226de573\" target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[中資]<br />\n（二）於社區檢測中心接受檢測服務（名單：<a href=\"http://www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=2501f582\" target=\"_blank\">www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/</a>）[中資]<br />\n（三）於121間郵政局、20個港鐵站設置的自動派發機或醫院管理局47間指定普通科門診診所索取深喉唾液測試樣本收集包，並把樣本交回指定樣本收集點（派發點及時間，以及樣本收集點及時間：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=226de573\" target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[難確定，或有中資]<br />\n（四）於醫管局普通科門診診所按照醫管局醫護人員的指示接受檢測<br />\n（五）自行安排接受由衞生署認可，並可就檢測結果發出電話短訊通知的私營化驗所提供的檢測（名單：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FList_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=0c9583e5\" target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf</a>）<br />\n（六）使用衞生防護中心派發到相關指明地方的樣本瓶（如適用），並按有關指示交回已採樣本的檢測樣本收集瓶。</span>"},{"pid":"04579e529294f548e3f3a7f420050204b71f2442","tid":2462794,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>武肺民間資訊</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nK